trans-unit.source: Using the C5 Data Migration Extension | Microsoft Docs

seg-source.mrk: Using the C5 Data Migration Extension | Microsoft Docs

target.mrk: Používání rozšíření C5 Data Migration | Microsoft Docs

trans-unit.source: Use this extension to migrate customers, vendors, items, and general ledger accounts from Microsoft Dynamics C5 2012 to Business Central.

seg-source.mrk: Use this extension to migrate customers, vendors, items, and general ledger accounts from Microsoft Dynamics C5 2012 to Business Central.

target.mrk: Toto rozšíření slouží k migraci zákazníků, dodavatelů, položek a účtů hlavní knihy z Microsoft Dynamics C5 2012 do Business Central.

trans-unit.source: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, items, and your general ledger accounts from Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012 to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: This extension makes it easy to migrate customers, vendors, items, and your general ledger accounts from Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012 to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Toto rozšíření usnadňuje migraci zákazníků, dodavatelů, položek a účtů hlavní knihy z Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012 do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: You can also migrate historical entries for general ledger accounts.

seg-source.mrk: You can also migrate historical entries for general ledger accounts.

target.mrk: Lze také migrovat historické položky pro účty hlavní knihy.

trans-unit.source: The company in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] must not contain any data.

seg-source.mrk: The company in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] must not contain any data.

target.mrk: Společnost v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] nesmí obsahovat žádná data.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, after you start a migration, do not create customers, vendors, items, or accounts until the migration finishes.

seg-source.mrk: Additionally, after you start a migration, do not create customers, vendors, items, or accounts until the migration finishes.

target.mrk: Zároveň po spuštění migrace nevytvářejte zákazníky, dodavatele, položky nebo účty, dokud migrace neskončí.

trans-unit.source: If there are open transactions that use foreign currencies, the exchange rates for those currencies are also migrated.

seg-source.mrk: If there are open transactions that use foreign currencies, the exchange rates for those currencies are also migrated.

target.mrk: Pokud existují otevřené transakce, které používají cizí měny, migrují se také směnné kurzy pro tyto měny.

trans-unit.source: Other exchange rates are not migrated.

seg-source.mrk: Other exchange rates are not migrated.

trans-unit.source: Standard dimensions: Department, Cost Center, Purpose
Historical G/L transactions are treated a little differently.

seg-source.mrk: Historical G/L transactions are treated a little differently.

target.mrk: S historickými finančními transakcemi se zachází trochu jinak.

trans-unit.source: When you migrate data you set a **Current Period** parameter.

seg-source.mrk: When you migrate data you set a **Current Period** parameter.

target.mrk: Při migraci dat nastavíte parametr **Aktuální období**.

trans-unit.source: This parameter specifies how to process G/L transactions.

seg-source.mrk: This parameter specifies how to process G/L transactions.

target.mrk: Tento parametr určuje, jak zpracovat finanční transakce.

trans-unit.source: Transactions after this date are migrated individually.

seg-source.mrk: Transactions after this date are migrated individually.

target.mrk: Transakce po tomto datu se migrují jednotlivě.

trans-unit.source: Transactions before this date are aggregated per account and migrated as a single amount.

seg-source.mrk: Transactions before this date are aggregated per account and migrated as a single amount.

target.mrk: Transakce před tímto datem jsou agregovány na jeden účet a migrovány jako jedna částka.

trans-unit.source: For example, let's say there are transactions in 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and you specify January 01, 2017 in the Current Period field.

seg-source.mrk: For example, let's say there are transactions in 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and you specify January 01, 2017 in the Current Period field.

target.mrk: Řekněme například, že existují transakce v letech 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018 a do pole Aktuální období zadáte 01.01.2017.

trans-unit.source: For each account, amounts for transactions on or before December 31, 2106, will be aggregated in a single general journal line for each G/L account.

seg-source.mrk: For each account, amounts for transactions on or before December 31, 2106, will be aggregated in a single general journal line for each G/L account.

target.mrk: Pro každý finanční účet budou částky za transakce k 31. prosinci 2106 nebo dříve sloučeny do jediného řádku finančního deníku.

trans-unit.source: All trascations after this date will be migrated individually.

seg-source.mrk: All trascations after this date will be migrated individually.

target.mrk: Všechny transakce po tomto datu budou migrovány jednotlivě.

trans-unit.source: The largest file size you can upload to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] is 150 MB.

seg-source.mrk: The largest file size you can upload to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] is 150 MB.

target.mrk: Největší velikost souboru, který můžete nahrát do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], je 150 MB.

trans-unit.source: If the file you export from C5 is larger than that, consider migrating data in multiple files.

seg-source.mrk: If the file you export from C5 is larger than that, consider migrating data in multiple files.

target.mrk: Pokud je soubor exportovaný z C5 větší, zvažte migraci dat pomocí více souborů.

trans-unit.source: For example, export one or two types of entities from C5, such as customers and vendors, to a file, and then export items to another file, and so on.

seg-source.mrk: For example, export one or two types of entities from C5, such as customers and vendors, to a file, and then export items to another file, and so on.

target.mrk: Například exportujte jeden nebo dva typy entit z C5, jako jsou například zákazníci a dodavatelé, do jednoho souboru, a poté exportujte položky do jiného souboru atd.

trans-unit.source: You can import files individually in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: You can import files individually in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: There are just a few steps to export data from C5, and import it in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]:

seg-source.mrk: There are just a few steps to export data from C5, and import it in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]:

target.mrk: Je třeba učinit jen několik kroků k exportu dat z C5 a jejich importu do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]:

trans-unit.source: In C5, use the **Export Database** feature to export the data.

seg-source.mrk: In C5, use the **Export Database** feature to export the data.

target.mrk: V C5 exportujte data pomocí funkce **Export databáze**.

trans-unit.source: Then send the export folder to a compressed (zipped) folder.

seg-source.mrk: Then send the export folder to a compressed (zipped) folder.

target.mrk: Poté odešlete exportovanou složku do komprimované (zip) složky.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Data Migration**, and then choose **Data Migration**.

seg-source.mrk: In [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], choose the ![Lightbulb that opens the Tell Me feature](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Tell me what you want to do") icon, enter **Data Migration**, and then choose **Data Migration**.

target.mrk: V [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] vyberte ikonu ![Žárovky, která otevře funkci Řekněte mi](media/ui-search/search_small.png "Řekněte mi, co chcete dělat"), zadejte **Migrace Dat** a poté zvolte **Migrace Dat**.

trans-unit.source: Complete the steps in the assisted setup guide.

seg-source.mrk: Complete the steps in the assisted setup guide.

target.mrk: Proveďte kroky v průvodci asistovanou instalaci.

trans-unit.source: Make sure to choose **Import from Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012** as the data source.

seg-source.mrk: Make sure to choose **Import from Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012** as the data source.

target.mrk: Ujistěte se, že jako zdroj dat jste zvolili **Import z Microsoft Dynamcis C5 2012**.

trans-unit.source: Viewing the Status of the Migration

seg-source.mrk: Viewing the Status of the Migration

trans-unit.source: Use the **Data Migration Overview** page to monitor the success of the migration.

seg-source.mrk: Use the **Data Migration Overview** page to monitor the success of the migration.

target.mrk: Na stránce **Přehled migrace dat** můžete sledovat úspěšnost migrace.

trans-unit.source: The page shows information such as the number of entities that the migration will include, the status of the migration, and the number of items that have been migrated and whether they were successfull.

seg-source.mrk: The page shows information such as the number of entities that the migration will include, the status of the migration, and the number of items that have been migrated and whether they were successfull.

target.mrk: Stránka zobrazuje informace, jako je počet entit, které bude migrace zahrnovat, stav migrace a počet položek, které byly migrovány, a zda byly jejich migrace úspěšné.

trans-unit.source: It also shows the number of errors, lets you investigate what went wrong and, when possible, makes it easy to go to the entity to fix the issues.

seg-source.mrk: It also shows the number of errors, lets you investigate what went wrong and, when possible, makes it easy to go to the entity to fix the issues.

target.mrk: Ukazuje také počet chyb, umožňuje vám zjistit, co se pokazilo, a pokud je to možné, usnadňuje přístup k entitě a řešení jejích problémů.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the next section in this topic.

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see the next section in this topic.

target.mrk: Další informace naleznete v další části tohoto tématu.

trans-unit.source: While you are waiting for the results of the migration, you must refresh the page to display the results.

seg-source.mrk: While you are waiting for the results of the migration, you must refresh the page to display the results.

target.mrk: Zatímco čekáte na výsledky migrace, musíte stránku aktualizovat, aby se zobrazily výsledky.

trans-unit.source: To help avoid double-posting to the general ledger, the following balance accounts are used for open transactions:

seg-source.mrk: To help avoid double-posting to the general ledger, the following balance accounts are used for open transactions:

target.mrk: Abychom se vyhnuli dvojímu účtování do hlavní knihy, pro otevřené transakce se používají následující rozvahové účty:

trans-unit.source: For vendors, we use the A/P account from the vendor posting group.

seg-source.mrk: For vendors, we use the A/P account from the vendor posting group.

target.mrk: Pro dodavatele používáme A/P účet z účto skupiny dodavatelů.

trans-unit.source: For customers, we use the A/R account from the customer posting group.

seg-source.mrk: For customers, we use the A/R account from the customer posting group.

target.mrk: Pro zákazníky používáme A/R účet z účto skupiny zákazníků.

trans-unit.source: For items, we create a general posting setup where the adjustment account is the account specified as the inventory account on the inventory posting setup.

seg-source.mrk: For items, we create a general posting setup where the adjustment account is the account specified as the inventory account on the inventory posting setup.

target.mrk: U položek vytváříme nastavení obecného účtování tam, kde účet adjustace je účet určený jako účet inventáře v nastavení účtování zásob.

trans-unit.source: If something goes wrong and an error occurs, the **Status** field will show **Completed with Errors**, and the **Error Count** field will show how many.

seg-source.mrk: If something goes wrong and an error occurs, the **Status** field will show **Completed with Errors**, and the **Error Count** field will show how many.

target.mrk: Pokud se něco pokazí a dojde k chybě, v poli **Stav** se zobrazí **Dokončeno s chybami** a v poli **Počet chyb** se zobrazí jejich počet.

trans-unit.source: To view a list of the errors, you can open the **Data Migration Errors** page by choosing:

seg-source.mrk: To view a list of the errors, you can open the **Data Migration Errors** page by choosing:

target.mrk: Chcete-li zobrazit seznam chyb, můžete otevřít stránku **Chyby dat migrace** výběrem:

trans-unit.source: The number in the **Error Count** field for the entity.

seg-source.mrk: The number in the **Error Count** field for the entity.

target.mrk: Číslo v poli **Počet chyb** pro entitu.

trans-unit.source: The entity, and then the **Show Errors** action.

seg-source.mrk: The entity, and then the **Show Errors** action.

target.mrk: Zvolením entity a potom akce **Zobrazit chyby**.

trans-unit.source: On the **Data Migration Errors** page, to fix an error you can choose an error message, and then choose **Edit Record** to view the migrated data for the entity.

seg-source.mrk: On the **Data Migration Errors** page, to fix an error you can choose an error message, and then choose **Edit Record** to view the migrated data for the entity.

target.mrk: Na stránce **Chyby dat migrace** můžete opravit chybu tak, že si vyberete chybovou zprávu a poté zvolíte **Upravit záznam**, čímž se zobrazí migrovaná data pro entitu.

trans-unit.source: If you have several errors to fix, you can choose **Bulk-Fix Errors** to edit the entities in a list.

seg-source.mrk: If you have several errors to fix, you can choose **Bulk-Fix Errors** to edit the entities in a list.

target.mrk: Pokud máte několik chyb k opravě, můžete použít možnost **Hromadné opravy chyb** a upravit entity v seznamu.

trans-unit.source: You still need to open individual records if the error was caused by a related entry though.

seg-source.mrk: You still need to open individual records if the error was caused by a related entry though.

target.mrk: Stále však musíte otevírat jednotlivé záznamy, pokud byla chyba způsobena související položkou.

trans-unit.source: For example, a vendor will not be migrated if an email address one of their contacts has an invalid format.

seg-source.mrk: For example, a vendor will not be migrated if an email address one of their contacts has an invalid format.

target.mrk: Například dodavatel nebude migrován, pokud má e-mailová adresa jednoho z jeho kontaktů neplatný formát.

trans-unit.source: After you fix one or more errors, you can choose **Migrate** to migrate only the entities you fixed, without having to completely restart the migration.

seg-source.mrk: After you fix one or more errors, you can choose **Migrate** to migrate only the entities you fixed, without having to completely restart the migration.

target.mrk: Po opravě jedné nebo více chyb můžete zvolit **Migrovat** a migrovat pouze entity, které jste opravili, aniž byste museli migraci úplně restartovat.

trans-unit.source: If you have fixed more than one error, you can use the **Select More** feature to select multiple lines to migrate.

seg-source.mrk: If you have fixed more than one error, you can use the **Select More** feature to select multiple lines to migrate.

target.mrk: Pokud jste opravili více než jednu chybu, můžete pomocí funkce **Vybrat více** vybrat více řádků pro migraci.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, if there are errors that are not important to fix, you can choose them and then choose **Skip Selections**.

seg-source.mrk: Alternatively, if there are errors that are not important to fix, you can choose them and then choose **Skip Selections**.

target.mrk: Alternativně, pokud existují chyby, u kterých oprava není důležitá, můžete je vybrat a poté zvolit **Přeskočit výběr**.

trans-unit.source: If you have items that are included in a BOM, you might need to migrate more than once if the original item is not created before the variants that reference it.

seg-source.mrk: If you have items that are included in a BOM, you might need to migrate more than once if the original item is not created before the variants that reference it.

target.mrk: Pokud máte položky, které jsou součástí kusovníku, možná je budete muset migrovat více než jednou, pokud původní položka není vytvořena před variantami, které na ni odkazují.

trans-unit.source: If an item variant is created first, the reference to the original item can cause an error message.

seg-source.mrk: If an item variant is created first, the reference to the original item can cause an error message.

target.mrk: Pokud je varianta položky vytvořena jako první, může odkaz na původní položku způsobit chybovou zprávu.

trans-unit.source: One way to verify that your data migrated correctly is to look at the following pages in C5 and [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: One way to verify that your data migrated correctly is to look at the following pages in C5 and [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Jedním ze způsobů, jak ověřit, zda vaše data byla správně migrována, je podívat se na následující stránky v C5 a [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: You can stop migrating data by choosing **Stop All Migrations**.

seg-source.mrk: You can stop migrating data by choosing **Stop All Migrations**.

target.mrk: Migraci dat můžete zastavit výběrem **Zastavit všechny migrace**.

trans-unit.source: If you do, all pending migrations are also stopped.

seg-source.mrk: If you do, all pending migrations are also stopped.

target.mrk: Pokud tak učiníte, zastaví se také všechny čekající migrace.
